_sText:
This is a remake of the map glock_tok_remake from TEMEY (http://www.fpsbanana.com/maps/20504). Its a middle sized gungame map with simpsons textures.

I've added simpsons textures, a custom skybox, some spawnpoints and make some other small changes.

Happy Fragging! Have Fun!

Skybox and nav file are included with pakrat!

The Map will be played on our server http://www.fpsbanana.com/servers/2098 sometimes.

Special thanks to
mck-76 for textures
Karatek√§fer for skybox
TEMEY for original map

The download file contains four *.jpg screenshots, a *.bz2 for your fastdownload and the bsp file.
